  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Category: Clan</p><p>Prerequisite: Fuma Clan, Level 12+</p><p>Your ability to never miss has become stuff of legends that even other Fuma's gossip about. You gain the following Benefits;</p><p>• You gain two additional uses of your Razor-Sharp Senses clan feature, per long rest.</p><p>• You can spend a use of Razor-Sharp Senses clan feature to maximize your weapons damage die.</p><p>• As a bonus action, you may call your next shot, by selecting one creature whom you can see within 60 feet. The first ranged weapon or taijutsu attack that deals weapon damage from a weapon with the thrown property that you make, is treated as a critical hit. You may do this twice per long rest</p>",
